Key looks up at Firestorm. Oh well, she thinks to herself, Liono doesn't 
want her anyways. He didn't want her enough to ask her not to participate in 
the next battle.

"Right now I'm being mad at Liono," she says, "Unless you have something 
better we can do..."

She smiles at him, moving seductively past him and off farther into the 
forest.
